    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "goss_code_text",
      "x": 545,
      "y": 410,
      "width": 370,
      "height": 170,
      "text": "GOSS: Gradient-based One-Side Sampling\n  1. Keep top a% (large |gradient|)\n  2. Random sample b% from rest\n  3. Upweight sampled by (1-a)/b\n  \u2192 keeps hard examples, subsamples easy\n\nEFB: Exclusive Feature Bundling\n  Sparse features that rarely co-occur\n  \u2192 bundled into single feature\n  \u2192 reduces #features via graph coloring",
      "originalText": "GOSS: Gradient-based One-Side Sampling\n  1. Keep top a% (large |gradient|)\n  2. Random sample b% from rest\n  3. Upweight sampled by (1-a)/b\n  \u2192 keeps hard examples, subsamples easy\n\nEFB: Exclusive Feature Bundling\n  Sparse features that rarely co-occur\n  \u2192 bundled into single feature\n  \u2192 reduces #features via graph coloring",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
